===== Involved rules descriptions:

[iamf][Rule #14] id: assert-audio-frame-obu
Section 3.9
Audio Frame OBU checks:
- When obu_type = OBU_IA_Audio_Frame, explicit_audio_substream_id SHALL be greater than 17.
- AudioFrameOBU SHALL refer to a valid audio_substream_id declared in an Audio Element OBU.
- There SHALL be exactly one Audio Element OBU with a given audio_substream_id in a set of Descriptors.

